<Content>For Travellers ...Not Tourists.... If you want to be part of the Mexico City scene, then the Ambassador Hotel is for you. Clean and reasonable, friendly staff, and a bar that is right out of the movie set of Casablanca. Old world comfort.This is a hotel for travellers, not tourists. If you enjoy immersing yourself in the culture that you are visiting, then the Hotel Ambassador is a great place to stay.If you want to be an American with Americans, than stay at the Sheraton. 
